snippet.title: Hikikomori life - Trailer
snippet.description:
Adventures of a reclusive gamer with elements of a simulator, quest and roguelike. Explore parallel worlds in an attempt to remove the curse from a magician in the body of a cat. Conquer a changing dungeon with many enemies. In the real world, equip a home, create objects, cook food, travel.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1597800/Hikikomori_life
Itch.io: https://pakodev.itch.io/hikikomori-life
